metadata.description: Generative Art Collection by Ryo Konishi. This collection comes with a variety of benefits and access to utilities.  The benefits include…   【Ryo Konishi DAO】 The owner of this NFT has...  - access to Ryo Konishi DAO's MERCHANDISE channel.  - access to Ryo Konishi DAO's MTG TABLE channel.  - join Ryo Konishi DAO's BEACH CLUB (IRL community).  What is Ryo Konishi DAO? Ryo Konishi DAO is a self-sustaining, decentralized art studio by a group of artists who enjoy activities that increase their individual influence through activities that enhance the value of the NFTs produced by DAO.     【Gogh Land】 This NFT owner is...  - entitled to use the Premium Bob Lennon Emote in Gogh Land.  - entitled to use Premium My Gallery in Gogh Land.  - access to the Gogh Land Labo.  What is Gogh Land? Gogh Land is a social networking NFT metaverse.  It is currently under development and scheduled to launch in 2024. Please join us at Ryo Konishi DAO to see the progress of development.    Please contact us → https://discord.gg/mafG5yuFRU
